img(inline src='src/assets/images/icon-workspace.svg')

p.-text
  | Tabs are used to navigate between views within the same context.

h3 Examples
p.-text
  | To display tabs, apply the class <code>a-tabs</code> to a <code>ul</code>. Wrap the tab
  | links in <code>li</code> tags and signify the active link with class <code>-active</code>.

h4 Horizontal
.example.-mb3
  .-p3.-pb4
    ul.a-tabs
      li.-active
        a(href='#') Active Tab
      li
        a(href='#') Tab Link
      li
        a(href='#') Tab Link
  :code(lang='html')
    <ul class="a-tabs">
      <li class="-active">
        <a href="#">Active Tab</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="#">Tab Link</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="#">Tab Link</a>
      </li>
    </ul>

